  "title": "Senior Recruitment Consultant (Robinson Road / Hybrid)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities :</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Engage in full cycle of recruitment process</li>\n  <li>Accountable for sourcing, conducting interviews and assess job applicants in accordance to clients' needs and requirements</li>\n  <li>Coordinate interviews between clients and candidates</li>\n  <li>Managing job offer process and negotiating salary package</li>\n  <li>Deliver positive candidate experience and act as career advisor to candidates</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All pplications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No. 20C0270</p>",
